WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.500
A day on the water with BlindSail, San Francisco Bay, June thirteenth.

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:11.700
Morning at the Oakland Yacht Club.

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:15.700
An all-volunteer crew, ready to cast off.

00:00:15.700 --> 00:00:20.200
Heading out past the Port of Oakland cranes.

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:28.200
Lines off, and we are underway.

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:32.200
Hands on the sheet, hauling it in.

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:36.200
And pure joy on the water.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:40.200
Steering the bay as the ferries slide past.

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:44.200
Right under the bridge — thumbs up.

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:48.200
Sailing home along the span.
